---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy information for the Veedyoo public landing site." path="/privacy/">
  <main class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[900px] px-4 py-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <p class="metadata text-[10px] text-coral">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-4xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="content-prose mt-8">
      <p>Veedyoo.com is a static public landing site. It is designed to explain the product and link visitors to the Veedyoo studio app.</p>
      <h2>Information collected on this site</h2>
      <p>This Phase 1 landing site does not include contact forms, newsletter forms, checkout, or account management. Account creation happens on app.veedyoo.com.</p>
      <h2>External links</h2>
      <p>When you click a call to action, you may leave veedyoo.com and open app.veedyoo.com. The app may have its own authentication and account handling.</p>
      <h2>Updates</h2>
      <p>This page should be updated before adding analytics, forms, tracking pixels, payments, or any feature that collects personal information on the public site.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
